Package info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.iresource_source.exceptions

Contains exceptions thrown by IResourceSource.

See: Description

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    OutOfResourceException
    Exception thrown by methods of implementations of IResourceSource when client tries to access resource that is not available but will become available later (the client may use IResourceSource.onAvailable(IPoorAction) to wait for resource).
